{"id": "ChIJLz5MuTq_woARNr7ORKQW7-4", "rating": 4.3, "priceLevel": "PRICE_LEVEL_VERY_EXPENSIVE", "userRatingCount": 679, "displayName": {"text": "Gwen", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJLz5MuTq_woARNr7ORKQW7-4/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21jMVVtdFFUVlIwYjFwTVMyNVhOSGhIYVRkV1kxRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "5 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "It’s that environment when at the restaurant the taste of each bite makes you give a small satisfying nod. You close your eyes and breathe out heavily - mumbling “Oh that’s SO good!”\nAnd not only you. It’s a collective act that I have experienced while dinning this evening at Gwen.\n\nI made a terrific choice with this place as they’ve put care and fantastic flavours in all the courses. Alongside a glass of Barbaresco and the flat iron with mouth-melting texture, this evening was delicious beginning to the end.\n\nChose the Piemonte region after a wine tasting with Country :) hoping that my next time here there will be white truffles season for the menu :)\n\nMy most fav was the chicken consommée with shiitake and chives though :) DELICIOUS! But all the appetizers were amazing. On the house also :)\n\nAnd… the knives selection!! Absolute WOW! I picked Nashville Tennessee origins Damascus steel. Gorgeous and sharp :)\n\nDon’t remember the dessert details but it was delicious and had some cinnamon with it. Hopefully the restaurant will describe it again for us :)\n\nAmazing treatment by Audrey, who carried me through my evening at Gwen, taking the time to explain the dishes and helping me decide. The entire staff was very friendly. Thanks for the wonderful evening!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "It’s that environment when at the restaurant the taste of each bite makes you give a small satisfying nod. You close your eyes and breathe out heavily - mumbling “Oh that’s SO good!”\nAnd not only you. It’s a collective act that I have experienced while dinning this evening at Gwen.\n\nI made a terrific choice with this place as they’ve put care and fantastic flavours in all the courses. Alongside a glass of Barbaresco and the flat iron with mouth-melting texture, this evening was delicious beginning to the end.\n\nChose the Piemonte region after a wine tasting with Country :) hoping that my next time here there will be white truffles season for the menu :)\n\nMy most fav was the chicken consommée with shiitake and chives though :) DELICIOUS! But all the appetizers were amazing. On the house also :)\n\nAnd… the knives selection!! Absolute WOW! I picked Nashville Tennessee origins Damascus steel. Gorgeous and sharp :)\n\nDon’t remember the dessert details but it was delicious and had some cinnamon with it. Hopefully the restaurant will describe it again for us :)\n\nAmazing treatment by Audrey, who carried me through my evening at Gwen, taking the time to explain the dishes and helping me decide. The entire staff was very friendly. Thanks for the wonderful evening!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Silvia Pompieru", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/108354841440443036546/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV1TqH0AkCM2B_hcOI6jQ2aR5a-fwBktdzlId7m8ukCRVYrCSjy=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2026-01-21T06:24:23.867685345Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21jMVVtdFFUVlIwYjFwTVMyNVhOSGhIYVRkV1kxRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21jMVVtdFFUVlIwYjFwTVMyNVhOSGhIYVRkV1kxRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2bf3ab94c3e2f:0xeeef16a444cebe36"}, {"name": "places/ChIJLz5MuTq_woARNr7ORKQW7-4/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25WdFZXSmhkV2swTVd4VFNETTNYemx5T1dWT2VFRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "5 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "I loved my meal here, everything was delicious and the service was wonderful! My favorite items were the lobster ravioli (must order), the flat iron steak, and the side of creamed leeks & onions. We ordered a decent amount of food and they paced it out really well even though we had a later reservation time. I would definitely come back again!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "I loved my meal here, everything was delicious and the service was wonderful! My favorite items were the lobster ravioli (must order), the flat iron steak, and the side of creamed leeks & onions. We ordered a decent amount of food and they paced it out really well even though we had a later reservation time. I would definitely come back again!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Katelyn", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/104769498789975520382/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUt60tZiChHXs6If6KvEJwaCMCDsPW5Ii1D4tqmUS3jEdSwIMYDiQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5"}, "publishTime": "2026-01-17T02:33:55.351178328Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25WdFZXSmhkV2swTVd4VFNETTNYemx5T1dWT2VFRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25WdFZXSmhkV2swTVd4VFNETTNYemx5T1dWT2VFRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2bf3ab94c3e2f:0xeeef16a444cebe36"}, {"name": "places/ChIJLz5MuTq_woARNr7ORKQW7-4/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21SS05rZDNibTl5VDJ0U2NubzROWGhuWlhoNFVYYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "4 months ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "Stopped here before going to a concert at the Dolby Theatre, had a great time! Recommend the chef's table if you can sit there, it's a great experience and the cooks are happy to answer any questions you have about their work.\n\nThe water menu was cute and the steak was absolutely on point!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Stopped here before going to a concert at the Dolby Theatre, had a great time! Recommend the chef's table if you can sit there, it's a great experience and the cooks are happy to answer any questions you have about their work.\n\nThe water menu was cute and the steak was absolutely on point!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "CC Mizrahi", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/103406702968373065599/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKdBRRAZeLLLaFC1gxOCnIvjvXC_FB5up2zjOmDdSY6WZz6wg=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5"}, "publishTime": "2026-02-18T01:33:49.187405029Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21SS05rZDNibTl5VDJ0U2NubzROWGhuWlhoNFVYYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21SS05rZDNibTl5VDJ0U2NubzROWGhuWlhoNFVYYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2bf3ab94c3e2f:0xeeef16a444cebe36"}, {"name": "places/ChIJLz5MuTq_woARNr7ORKQW7-4/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pNdE16Wk1iV1pxYWpCNVVVWlVjRUkwZFU1alJtYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "6 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Fantastic meal from start to finish. We came to celebrate my birthday and Gwen did not disappoint. Loved the dining room and our comfortable booth. Our server was great - friendly and skillfully guided us through the menu. The food was uniformly delicious. Highlights were the table bread and butter, fresh oysters, lamb ribs, lobster ravioli, duck fat potatoes and bone in ribeye. Cocktails were excellent as well. Loved this place.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Fantastic meal from start to finish. We came to celebrate my birthday and Gwen did not disappoint. Loved the dining room and our comfortable booth. Our server was great - friendly and skillfully guided us through the menu. The food was uniformly delicious. Highlights were the table bread and butter, fresh oysters, lamb ribs, lobster ravioli, duck fat potatoes and bone in ribeye. Cocktails were excellent as well. Loved this place.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "John O", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/102788004063565192614/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVjH3bODE-J3xTiMAIkcMruO0MvMONA1FBalYguFQHRyKx7vD2T4Q=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6"}, "publishTime": "2026-01-05T21:40:46.035501304Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pNdE16Wk1iV1pxYWpCNVVVWlVjRUkwZFU1alJtYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pNdE16Wk1iV1pxYWpCNVVVWlVjRUkwZFU1alJtYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2bf3ab94c3e2f:0xeeef16a444cebe36"}, {"name": "places/ChIJLz5MuTq_woARNr7ORKQW7-4/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tGcFpIZHJiMHhpZFRoMU0yTjNUVEpFWldSdVUyYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Recently went back to Gwen to take my parents. Was here a few months earlier for our anniversary and it was one of the best meals of our lives. They rotate their menu and though still great, this second time the food was less impressive.  Perhaps it’s because the first time we sat at the chefs counter (12/10 experience!) while the second time was at a standard table (8/10)? Not sure! Either way highly recommend Gwen which has been 10/10 in average.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Recently went back to Gwen to take my parents. Was here a few months earlier for our anniversary and it was one of the best meals of our lives. They rotate their menu and though still great, this second time the food was less impressive.  Perhaps it’s because the first time we sat at the chefs counter (12/10 experience!) while the second time was at a standard table (8/10)? Not sure! Either way highly recommend Gwen which has been 10/10 in average.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Carlos Bolanos", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/105349806647713366836/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUx-27zntS-oIWGVhUMlnRHYMtsL0ugR_Jns5OpSawb2S6Emumx=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba2"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-08T03:25:30.801162957Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tGcFpIZHJiMHhpZFRoMU0yTjNUVEpFWldSdVUyYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tGcFpIZHJiMHhpZFRoMU0yTjNUVEpFWldSdVUyYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2bf3ab94c3e2f:0xeeef16a444cebe36"}], "photos": [{"name": "places/ChIJLz5MuTq_woARNr7ORKQW7-4/photos/AWCwydjXJymvcU_-9yJfqt5sopl5oqoCV_IIhizWs_Bigs8uU5t22JsNrjltBxbuGMtxQFbHmAH8BsT3the0I4H9b-OWuTwNvQtO1882Jg7P2ijsUmaeGnBlS1RfSIpEgp6ReH_0sHKKf8ZqNTTBHNnRG-sPxxY9N5KLsz3rkLWFz1i56fP6YP8tC69ErlLIfuZyZq-4ssrXikUIUujM9KTfkL_N4kca0SgIvDVUDC-5NGQ5Y7bnDM5iDL7m6wL9g_z4Wi24bITQLN2sT3kNuC7XXdHAsxywKD2bsIHREdJQvkvW1eSp2GyoiNimmsL5SQgWvu3jNlTsD6qQXSgTQv3lIv5YWIG6o8Lo8YboYRvgnTY8hf1M6pPdPNl7M8nx0Jh1p655PZDmmqrV8QaxVWq1hKFi4zjAiHMPXHdU-eweAA6Z2g", "widthPx": 2048, "heightPx": 1367, "authorAttributions": [{"displayName": "Gwen", "uri": "https://maps.google.com/maps/contrib/104072149597339382330", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXtOY0fyTtqKqJRyeJQ7F8wH0weYWxrB76SwwSsIuNDwf-Qc9M=s100-p-k-no-mo"}], "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=!1e10!2sCIHM0ogKEICAgICam4HQGA&t=27&cb_client=maps_api_places.places_api&hl=en-US", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/place//data=!3m4!1e2!3m2!1sCIHM0ogKEICAgICam4HQGA!2e10!4m2!3m1!1s0x80c2bf3ab94c3e2f:0xeeef16a444cebe36"}, {"name": "places/ChIJLz5MuTq_woARNr7ORKQW7-4/photos/AWCwydh6M4iX0mV5onKQRfszZzmoxMQT-HSlLEL7TVyRDTJW6EMlwgvsDnJsyc5ouIpkPZsxsbQzB0hy_vvhPmIFDTz7UobTckQagnOm2oh1-a0SgnCcNaW54Ve5P5nyfCLh8ERCxQpe8sigjIYcpnC836sF_h-gI_NwUqsZIHGVnmIpfOoCfC3ZDQ8R2Y2NPKpDmj19Xi4rKqA8CeV1XHblVWZSEhLK45EU8lO-4v-9WiD-mH3T_j2tDZqck8Vm5jyGIo90RrIwiDfMoMPHM67YJBBhiMZF